- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel Residual Attention Graph Convolutional Network. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with a challenging task that requires advanced AI techniques. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with 3D scene classification and exploits intrinsic geometric context inside a 3D space. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with 3D scene classification using RGB-D sensors, which are commonly used in robotics applications.
